                                        "Text": "Welcome to the first session of MindTrails! Today you'll complete 10 short training scenarios from a domain that you'll select in a few minutes. Next, you'll do 5 training scenarios that are from different domains. This will help you learn to apply your flexible thinking skills to lots of different types of situations. Last, you'll complete a brief exercise. "
