                {
                    "Name": "Questions",
                    "Title": "Three Brief Questions",
                    "Type": "Exercise",
                    "Pages": [
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Thinking about the last 24 hours, how anxious have you felt? \n\n0 = Most calm I could imagine being. \n\n10 = Most anxious, panicked, or scared I could imagine being."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Slider",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Minimum": 0,
                                        "Maximum": 10,
                                        "OtherChoices": [
                                            "Prefer not to answer."
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Thinking about the last 24 hours, how much were you able to change the way you thought about things when you wanted to feel better? \n\nAn example might be: If you were feeling worried about an upcoming test, were you able to remind yourself that you studied a lot and were prepared? \n\n0 = Not at all - I wasn't able to think in different ways to feel better. \n\n10 = Completely - I was totally able to think in different ways to feel better. "
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Slider",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Minimum": 0,
                                        "Maximum": 10,
                                        "OtherChoices": [
                                            "I didn't want\\need to change my feelings",
                                            " I'm not sure",
                                            "Prefer not to answer."
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Thinking about the last 24 hours, how much did you try to stay away from or be less involved in situations that would make you anxious or scared? \n\nAn example might be: If your teacher asked a question to the class and you knew the answer, do you not answer so you won't draw attention to yourself? \n\n0 = I tried to stay away from doing anything and everything that would make me anxious or scared. \n\n10 = If there was something that would make me anxious or scared, I pushed myself to do it anyway."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Slider",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Minimum": 0,
                                        "Maximum": 10,
                                        "OtherChoices": [
                                            "Nothing happened that made me anxious",
                                            "Prefer not to answer."
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "Name": "LemonExercise",
                    "Title": "Lemon Exercise",
                    "Type": "Exercise",
                    "Pages": [
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "The purpose of this quick exercise is to demonstrate what imagination-based thinking is. You will imagine what seeing, touching, and smelling a lemon is like. Please imagine this as if you are really experiencing it."
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "In this exercise--and throughout the training program--please remember to imagine what is happening through your own eyes, similar to the picture on the left. This is more effective than viewing the situation as an outside observer, like the picture on the right."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic1.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Okay...let's begin! Imagine you are holding the lemon in your right hand, and you can feel its shape and its weight."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic2.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Now imagine you are shining a light on the lemon, and you can see the waxy and lumpy texture of the yellow skin."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic3.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Now imagine that you scratch the skin with your fingernail, then you bring the lemon up to your nose, and you can smell the fresh zesty juice from the skin."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic4.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Now imagine that you cut the lemon in half, and you bring one half of it up for a closer look. You can see the juicy flesh in the shape of segments that look like a wagon wheel."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic5.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Now imagine that you squeeze the lemon and some of the juice squirts right into your eyes, and it is really stinging, making your eyes water."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic6.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 2,
                            "ShowButtons": "AfterTimeout",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "That was the Lemon Exercise! Don't worry if you didn't experience all of the sensations strongly. This is completely normal."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Media",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "ImageUrl": "https://github.com/TeachmanLab/MindtrailsMobile_Resources/raw/main/bbbs/protocols/protocol1/media/images/lemon/pic7.jpeg",
                                        "ImageType": "image/jpeg",
                                        "ImageFramed": "true"
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                },
                {
                    "Name": "UsingYourImagination",
                    "Title": "Using Your Imagination",
                    "Type": "Exercise",
                    "Pages": [
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "In this exercise, please think of an UPCOMING situation that you expect will make you feel anxious, worried, or scared. Pick a situation that you worry might go badly, or that you expect will bring on feelings of anxiety (like racing heart, sweating). Any situation that will make you feel quite anxious or scared will work, as long as it is a situation that is likely to actually happen."
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Please describe the situation in a few words:"
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Entry"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Please imagine the situation as vividly as possible (i.e., so that it feels very real). Try to imagine you are actually in the situation. Play out the specific parts of the situation in your head. Try to imagine using all your senses while you think about this situation. Think about the things you would see, hear, and smell if you were really in that situation. Think about the kinds of things you would think or feel if you were actually there."
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 20,
                            "ShowButtons": "Never",
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Play this situation in your head for the next 20 seconds. \n\nThe screen will change in 20 seconds. "
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "How anxious did you feel (at the highest level of anxiety) as you completed the imagery task?  \n\n0 = Absolutely no anxiety. \n\n10 = Totally anxious."
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Slider",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Minimum": 0,
                                        "Maximum": 10,
                                        "OtherChoices": [
                                            "Prefer not to answer."
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "How vividly did you imagine the situation?"
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Buttons",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Buttons": [
                                            "Not at all vivid",
                                            "Somewhat vivid",
                                            "Moderately vivid",
                                            "Very vivid",
                                            "Totally vivid",
                                            "Prefer not to answer"
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "How likely is it that the situation or task will turn out well versus turn out badly?"
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Buttons",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Buttons": [
                                            "Very likely to turn out well",
                                            "Somewhat likely to turn out well",
                                            "Neutral",
                                            "Somewhat likely to turn out badly",
                                            "Very likely to turn out badly",
                                            "Prefer not to answer"
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "If this situation did turn out badly, how well or badly would you be able to handle it?"
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Buttons",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Buttons": [
                                            "Very well",
                                            "Somewhat well",
                                            "Neutral",
                                            "Somewhat badly",
                                            "Very badly",
                                            "Prefer not to answer"
                                        ]
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
                }
            ]
