                    "Name": "PredictTheFuture",
                    "Title": "Predict the Future",
                    "Type": "Exercise",
                    "Pages": [
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "On the next screen, you will be asked to write about a possible upcoming event in your life, or something that you are worried might happen. Before pressing NEXT, please think about a situation that might happen over the next week when you will feel anxious, scared, or worried. This can be a situation that makes you anxious a lot, or something that doesn't happen a lot. \n \nAs you think of an event, try to really see yourself in the situation. Where are you? What day of the week is it? What time is it? Who is around you? What are you doing? How do you feel? \n \nAfter you come up with your situation, please press NEXT. \n \nExamples could include taking a test, talking to strangers, using social media, dealing with family or friends, or whatever makes you feel anxious. "
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Please take a moment to write one or two sentences to describe the situation.\n \nPress next when you are ready to continue. "
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Entry"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 30,
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "For the next 30 seconds, please picture yourself in the situation you just described. The screen will change automatically in 30 seconds. "
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Timeout": 90,
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Now, take the next 90 seconds to think of as many different thoughts that you could have in the situation as you can. These thoughts can be negative or positive. Be as creative as possible with all of the different thoughts you could have while you're in the situation that makes you anxious, especially thoughts that would help you feel less anxious. \n\nPlease type each of the thoughts in the box below. You can put each thought on a new line. \n\nThe screen will change after 90 seconds. "
                                    }
                                },
                                {
                                    "Type": "Entry"
                                }
                            ]
                        },
                        {
                            "Inputs": [
                                {
                                    "Type": "Text",
                                    "Parameters": {
                                        "Text": "Great job! You predicted the future! Now, if your situation happens over the next week, you can have a lot of different thoughts come into your mind. Try to remember some of your thoughts that make you feel less anxious! "
                                    }
                                }
                            ]
                        }
                    ]
